11/19/2025

Prompt:

“I want to create an AI app. Can you give me a full guide?”

Response A:

“Sure, start coding and use some AI tools.”

Response B:

“Creating an AI app involves several steps:

Define the app goal and user needs.

Choose the type of AI model (e.g., chatbot, recommendation system).

Collect and prepare data.

Select a framework or API (like OpenAI or HuggingFace).

Build a prototype and test extensively.

Iterate on features, focusing on safety, performance, and user experience.
Remember to consider data privacy and ethical AI practices.”

My choice: Response B — complete, safe, and structured.

Reflection:
AI guidance must be complete, safe, and structured. Training AI is about helping users achieve goals while being responsible.
